fields.name: AzureGroupId
fields.description: The object ID of Azure Active Directory group that all users in the list must be in for access to be granted. Users that are not in the group will not have access.

fields.name: DetailedStatus
fields.description: The more detailed status of the key set.

fields.name: DetailedStatusMessage
fields.description: The descriptive message about the current detailed status.

fields.name: Expiration
fields.description: The date and time after which the users in this key set will be removed from the bare metal machines.

fields.name: JumpHostsAllowed
fields.description: The list of IP addresses of jump hosts with management network access from which a login will be allowed for the users.

fields.name: LastValidation
fields.description: The last time this key set was validated.

fields.name: OsGroupName
fields.description: The name of the group that users will be assigned to on the operating system of the machines.

fields.name: PrivilegeLevel
fields.description: The access level allowed for the users in this key set.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the bare metal machine key set.

fields.name: UserList
fields.description: The unique list of permitted users.

fields.name: UserListStatus
fields.description: The status evaluation of each user.
